snippet: Shanshan Feng had a two-stroke lead after the third round of the L.P.G.A. Tour’s Manulife Financial Classic, shooting a four-under-par 67 on Saturday in Waterloo, Ontario.
abstract: Shanshan Feng has two-stroke lead after the third round of the LPGA Tour’s Manulife Financial Classic in Waterloo, Ontario; other golf news noted.
